  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for postgresql18",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for postgresql18 fixes the following issue:\n\nUpdate to version 18.3 (bsc#1258754).\n\nRegression fixes:\n\n  - the substring() function raises an error 'invalid byte sequence for encoding' on non-ASCII text values if the\n    source of that value is a database column (caused by CVE-2026-2006 fix).\n  - a standby may halt and return an error 'could not access status of transaction'.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
